Title : Category:Hungary youth international footballers
Text : This category is for footballers who have appeared for the Hungary national youth football teams, which consists of the under-16, [[Hungary national under-17 football team|under-17]], under-18, [[Hungary national under-19 football team|under-19]] and [[Hungary national under-20 football team|under-20]] teams. Players in this category should also be left in [[:category:Hungarian footballers]].

